                content:
                  "Customizable tests made it perfect for our institution.",
              },
              {
                name: "Omkar",
                content:
                  "Seamless experience, from login to submission. 10/10!",
              },
              {
                name: "Dhanush",
                content: "It's a game changer for online assessments.",
              },
              {
                name: "Ayush",
                content:
                  "Detailed reports helped me identify weak areas instantly.",
              },
              {
                name: "Imran",
                content: "CAPE made it easy to organize and monitor exams.",
              },
              {
                name: "Yugal",
                content:
                  "Highly secure and perfect for institutions and students alike.",
              },
              {
                name: "Harshit",
                content:
